name: Flames
description:
In a family dinner during christmas, it is hard to comunicate and interact with people. So we end up, scrolling our phones, seeing so much and the same time feeling a deep emptiness. 
That night the forest were in fire for hours, every day bad news to share and nothing else we can do. Just wait it to the end...
the fire to extingish, the dinner to be eating so we can go home and the animals could find a new one.
Digital painting 1080x1080 300pp
